  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd   \u0ba4\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A man was arrested for pushing a member of the Pradeshiya Sabha into the market",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "During the violent incidents that took place in the Galle Mukathidal area last May 9, a person who robbed the wallet of a member of the Ambalangodai Divisional Council and pushed him into the bar was arrested by the Colombo Crime Squad.",
        "It has been reported that the suspect who was arrested at Kombanith Street is a 34-year-old resident of Thematagoda area.",
        "On the 9th of May, while the member of the local council was traveling in a bus, some people, including the arrested suspect, pulled the local council member down from the bus and robbed him of money, and pushed him into Bara Vavi."
      ],
